n","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-6","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"My bin has not been emptied, what should I do?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-6","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-5"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"Check to make sure the bin was due to be collected using our bin round lookup: ",["A",{"href":"https://selfservice.wychavon.gov.uk/wdcroundlookup/wdc_search.jsp","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener"},"Bin Round Lookup"],". If your bin was due to be collected, was it out by 7am? Was the right bin put out? Was a sticker left on your bin advising why it wasn’t collected?"],"\n",["P",{},"If the correct bin was presented by 7am and no sticker was left on your bin, please report a missed bin: ",["A",{"href":"https://selfservice.wychavon.gov.uk/sw2wasteandrecycling/wdc_enquiryselect.jsp#?linkid=2","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener"},"Waste and Recycling Services."]]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-item"},"\n",["A",{"class":"el-title uk-accordion-title","href":"","id":"uk-accordion-7","role":"button","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-8","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"I have been told that my bin is contaminated. What can I do now?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-8","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-7"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"Remove the contamination from your bin and present it for collection on your next collection day. You can take any additional waste to your local Household Recycling Centre - ",["A",{"href":"https://www.worcestershire.gov.uk/lets-waste-less/household-recycling-centres","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener"},"Household Recycling Centres | Worcestershire County Council."]]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-item"},"\n",["A",{"class":"el-title uk-accordion-title","href":"","id":"uk-accordion-9","role":"button","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-10","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"What if my bin is lost damaged or stolen?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-10","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-9"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"You can report that your bin is damaged or lost (and anything else waste and recycling related) online using our ",["A",{"href":"https://selfservice.wychavon.gov.uk/sw2wasteandrecycling/wdc_enquiryselect.jsp#?linkid=2","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener"},"Waste and Recycling Services "],"page."]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-item"},"\n",["A",{"class":"el-title uk-accordion-title","href":"","id":"uk-accordion-11","role":"button","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-12","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"What can I put in my black and green bins?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-12","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-11"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"Use our recycling search to find out what goes in which colour bin."],"\n",["P",{},["A",{"href":"/waste-and-recycling/recycling-search"},"Recycling Search "]],"\n",["P",{},"Plastic bottles and packaging (except black plastic), cans, tins, paper, card, glass bottles and jars can go in your green bin. Nappies do NOT go in your green bin."]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-item"},"\n",["A",{"class":"el-title uk-accordion-title","href":"","id":"uk-accordion-13","role":"button","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-14","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"Can I have another black bin?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-14","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-13"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"No. Each household is entitled to one black waste bin. Some households have managed to gain a second bin over the years and we are currently undertaking a project to remove these bins. If you meet a certain criteria, you may be entitled to a larger 240 litre bin but most households are entitled to a 180 litre black waste bin. If you believe you meet the criteria, you can request a larger bin using our ",["A",{"href":"https://selfservice.wychavon.gov.uk/sw2wasteandrecycling/wdc_enquiryselect.jsp#?linkid=2","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener"},"Waste and Recycling Services "],"page."]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-item"},"\n",["A",{"class":"el-title uk-accordion-title","href":"","id":"uk-accordion-15","role":"button","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-16","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"Can I have another green bin?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-16","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-15"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"We do allow residents to have an additional green recycling bin and this can be requested using our ",["A",{"href":"https://selfservice.wychavon.gov.uk/sw2wasteandrecycling/wdc_enquiryselect.jsp#?linkid=2","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener"},"Waste and Recycling Services "],"page."]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-item"},"\n",["A",{"class":"el-title uk-accordion-title","href":"","id":"uk-accordion-17","role":"button","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-18","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"Can I leave black sacks at the side of my bin for collection?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-18","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-17"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"No. Excess waste must be disposed of at one of the Household Waste and Recycling Centres. We do allow additional bags to be collected over the Christmas period."]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-item"},"\n",["A",{"class":"el-title uk-accordion-title","href":"","id":"uk-accordion-19","role":"button","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-20","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"What can I do to prevent maggots in my bin?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-20","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-19"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"Keeping your bin clean with the lid closed should prevent maggots. Food waste should be wrapped prior to disposal."]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-item"},"\n",["A",{"class":"el-title uk-accordion-title","href":"","id":"uk-accordion-21","role":"button","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-22","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"I have trouble moving my wheelie bins, can I get help?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-22","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-21"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"You can request an assisted collection, if you are unable to move your wheelie bins yourself. This can be done using our ",["A",{"href":"https://selfservice.wychavon.gov.uk/sw2wasteandrecycling/wdc_enquiryselect.jsp#?linkid=2","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener"},"Waste and Recycling Services "],"page."]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-item"},"\n",["A",{"class":"el-title uk-accordion-title","href":"","id":"uk-accordion-23","role":"button","aria-controls":"uk-accordion-24","aria-expanded":"false","aria-disabled":"false"},"Will the Council clean my bin?"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-accordion-content","hidden":"","id":"uk-accordion-24","role":"region","aria-labelledby":"uk-accordion-23"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"el-content uk-panel"},["P",{},"It is your responsibility to clean your bin. We do not offer a cleaning service or recommend any companies that carry out a service like this."]],"\n"],"\n"],"\n"],"\n"]]],"\n"],"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-section-default uk-section"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-container"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-grid tm-grid-expand uk-child-width-1-1 uk-grid-margin"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"uk-width-1-1"},"\n",["H1",{},"        Sort It Out! Game    "],["DIV",{"class":"uk-panel uk-margin"},["P",{},"Try our new, fun and interactive waste sorting game Sort It Out! "],"\n",["P",{},"Challenge yourself on how to recycle or dispose of materials correctly ranging from aluminium foil and egg shells to batteries and plastic bags."],"\n",["P",{},"Simply drag and drop the material to the stream of your choice, you’ll soon learn how much you really know."],"\n",["P",{},"Complete the levels successfully and you can select a special prize to help build your own digital park."],"\n",["P",{},"Try the game now!"]],["DIV",{"id":"page#4"},["IFRAME",{"__playwright_bounding_rect__":"{\"left\":30,\"top\":2740.765625,\"right\":770,\"bottom\":3340.765625}","src":""},"</</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</main>\n<footer>\n<!-- Builder #footer --><style class=\"uk-margin-remove-adjacent\">#footer\\#0 .el-item{margin:0px}#footer\\#0 .el-item:before{display:none}#footer\\#1 .uk-icon.uk-totop{color:#1A7BBC};</style>\n<div id=\"footer#1\" class=\"uk-section-primary uk-section uk-section-large\" uk-scrollspy=\"target: [uk-scrollspy-class]; cls: uk-animation-slide-bottom-small; delay: 50;\">\n<div class=\"uk-grid-margin-large uk-container uk-container-small\"><div class=\"uk-grid tm-grid-expand uk-grid-large\" uk-grid>\n<div class=\"uk-width-auto uk-width-1-2@s uk-width-1-4@m\">\n<h3 class=\"uk-h4\" uk-scrollspy-class> <a class=\"el-link uk-link-heading\" href=\"/about-wychavon-district-council\">About</a> </h3>\n<ul class=\"uk-list\" uk-scrollspy-class>\n<li class=\"el-item\"> <div class=\"el-content uk-panel\"><a href=\"/about-wychavon-district-council/equality-and-diversity\" class=\"el-link uk-link-text uk-margin-remove-last-child\">Equality & diversity</a></div> </li> <li class=\"el-item\"> <div class=\"el-content uk-panel\"><a href=\"/about-wychavon-district-council/privacy-notice\" class=\"el-link uk-link-text uk-margin-remove-last-child\">Privacy notice</a></div> </li> <li class=\"el-item\"> <div class=\"el-content uk-p